testBody: public static boolean test() throws Throwable { java.awt.geom.Rectangle2D rec = new java.awt.geom.Rectangle2D.Double(10, 20, 10, 2); java.awt.geom.Rectangle2D target = new java.awt.geom.Rectangle2D.Double(-22, 10, 2, 10); java.awt.geom.Rectangle2D result = rotateQuadrant(rec, 1); return (target.equals(result));}
